'''托尼·金'''（{{lang-en|Tony Kim}}<ref name="bbcnorthkoreanuniversitynames">{{cite news|title=North Korean university names detained US citizen|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-39689559|publisher=BBC News|date=April 24, 2017|accessdate=2021-01-10|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308062021/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-asia-39689559|dead-url=no}}</ref>，{{bd|1959年}} ）原名'''金相篤'''（{{lang-ko|김상덕}}），是一名韓裔[[美國|美國]]學者，曾在[[朝鮮|朝鮮]]被拘留382天。他是[[2016年朝鮮洪災|2016年朝鮮洪災]]受災地區運送外國援助物資的區域負責人，其在朝鮮的[[人道主義|人道主義]]工作已經進行了10多年。2017年4月22日，金和他的妻子被拘留，隨後金在[[平壤順安國際機場|平壤順安國際機場]]等待登機時被逮捕。2017年5月，金被指控“犯下旨在顛覆朝鮮政權的敵對行為”<ref>{{cite news|last1=Pearson|first1=James|last2=Park|first2=Ju-Min|title=North Korea detains third U.S. citizen: Yonhap'|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-northkorea-usa-detainee-idUSKBN17P038|accessdate=24 April 2018|date=23 April 2017|archive-date=2021-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210322124155/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-northkorea-usa-detainee-idUSKBN17P038|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Parke">{{cite web|url=http://www.foxnews.com/world/2018/02/12/miles-from-winter-olympics-three-americans-remain-detained-in-north-korea.html|title=Miles from Winter Olympics, three Americans remain detained in North Korea|first=Caleb|last=Parke|date=12 February 2018|publisher=|access-date=2021-01-10|archive-date=2018-08-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180819202525/http://www.foxnews.com/world/2018/02/12/miles-from-winter-olympics-three-americans-remain-detained-in-north-korea.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年5月9日，據報導，金相篤被釋放<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|url=https://www.cnn.com/2018/05/09/politics/mike-pompeo-north-korea-prisoners-tick-tock/index.html|title=Pompeo's 13 hours in North Korea|last=Gaouette|first=Nicole|date=2018-05-09|access-date=2018-05-11|archive-date=2021-04-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210430112324/https://www.cnn.com/2018/05/09/politics/mike-pompeo-north-korea-prisoners-tick-tock/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

